            719,
            149,
            733
        ],
        "page_idx": 6
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "监管链 global regulation blockchain",
        "bbox": [
            149,
            747,
            475,
            762
        ],
        "page_idx": 6
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "以全局服务和监管为目的构建的区块链系统。",
        "bbox": [
